<div class="design">
    <h1>Please sign this petition to make the
        <br />
        Habit of Not Flushing a Public Offense.</h1>
    <h5>If you ever entered a bathroom and felt disgusted by it's smell,
        <br />
        there is a big chance that that awful smell started because someone
        didn't flush.
        <br />
        It's time to make it stop. Please help us with your signature.
    </h5>
    <br /><br />
    <img class="pissoir" src="/toilet-censored.jpg" alt="" />
    <br />
    <h2> <u>Please Register to start flushing properly!</u> </h2>
    {{#if addUsersInfoError}}<h3>Something went wrong. Please register if you
            are new here or log in if you have already registered</h3>{{/if}}
    <form method="POST">
        <h3 class="login">If you have already registered, please
            <a class="click" href="/login"> login </a></h3>
        <div class="description">
            <h4>First Name</h4>
            <input
                type="text"
                id="first"
                name="first"
                placeholder=""
                value=""
                autocomplete="off"
                required
            />
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <h4>Last Name</h4>
            <input
                type="text"
                id="last"
                name="last"
                placeholder=""
                value=""
                autocomplete="off"
                required
            />
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <h4>Email Address</h4>
            <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                pattern="[^@\\\\\\\\\s]+@[^@\s]+\.[^@\s]+"
                name="email"
                placeholder=""
                value=""
                autocomplete="off"
                required
            />
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <h4>Password</h4>
            <input
                type="password"
                id="password"
                name="password"
                minlength="8"
                placeholder=""
                value=""
                autocomplete="off"
                required
            />
        </div>
        <br />
        <br />
        <button>Register</button>
    </form>

</div>
